        "created_at": "2019-04-13T04:53:05.563Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The cluster file stored at <code>/etc/foundationdb/fdb.cluster</code> contains cluster information and is automatically updated on the server when coordinators are added or removed.</p>\n<p>Does the cluster file also automatically get updated on clients? If so, when?</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 3,
        "updated_at": "2019-04-13T04:53:18.700Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
        "reply_to_post_number": null,
        "quote_count": 0,
